  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      This study aims to investigate the incidence and clinical course of colonoscopy related
      perforation based on the result of a prospective registry.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
  <detailed_description>
    <textblock>
      In each endoscopy unit from participating hospital, there is a alarm system focusing on the
      development of perforation. Therefore, perforation cases will not be missed from the
      registry.
    </textblock>
  </detailed_description>
